{"tid":1223980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家真係唔好攞宗教黎笑","createTime":"2019-06-15T00:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T07:06:44.000Z","uid":215677,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9244d1c227ed2268bc4e963163fea064e6c9f546","tid":1223980,"uid":215677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:52:35.000Z","msg":"我老母基督徒黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係一直都係民主派(雖然和理非但係都支持示威者行動嘅)<br />\n但佢見到呢句打救你已經覺得有啲反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我知大家好鐘意唱主能夠，但原本首歌係普通話歌詞黎，所以依家咁唱已經有啲基督徒表示反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以再小心啲啲，真係唔好攞宗教黎笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主能夠我都好鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可能3-4個圍住一隻狗咁撚化佢囉<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2H1G0jY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2H1G0jY.jpg&h=63a061ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b97943f117f88f2d70cafdaad7b8ae726f05937c","tid":1223980,"uid":59585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:56:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95406f0d8cfe52cc89e091c4bf4cdc55960b073e","tid":1223980,"uid":261530,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:02:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24054a9a2f28dfedb21c7263aff1687f87ee45c5","tid":1223980,"uid":222907,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ew0cSxpvAlE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dew0cSxpvAlE&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8EcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=17b6d4bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ew0cSxpvAlE</a><br />\n<br />\n好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440d2af1467130e2748ecf38dab4395f73845fc5","tid":1223980,"uid":259055,"like":4,"